本项目（SurviveNJU-CS）是一个公益性质的资源聚合平台，旨在为南京大学在校同学提供
学习参考。

本项目所引用的第三方内容（GitHub 仓库、网站链接等）的版权均归原作者所有，本项目
不重新分发任何受版权保护的内容，仅提供链接索引和简要介绍。

如任何被引用的内容作者希望从本项目中移除相关链接，请通过 GitHub Issue 联系维护团队，
我们将在合理时间内处理。

This project (SurviveNJU-CS) is a non-commercial, public-interest resource aggregation 
platform. All third-party content referenced herein (GitHub repositories, external links, etc.) 
remains the copyright of their respective owners. This project does not redistribute any 
copyrighted content but only provides link indexes and brief descriptions.

If any author whose content is referenced wishes to have it removed, please contact the 
maintainers via GitHub Issue and we will handle it in a timely manner.
